channel.title: Cleaned Delta oldschool 317 -RandQm
channel.description:
[center][size=14pt][b]edit: - 9 december 2011 TOTALLY NOT CLEANED! i wozz nub when doing this [/b][/size][/center]
[b]Sup, I started my own server (see sig) with an old delta source I found on my computer, After I downloaded iSkape I decided to mix them cuz I liked iSkape a lot. I cleaned it out for a part, then I came into contact with Zach, and Ive sent my cleaned version to him, That made me thinking, and put me on to Clean the source and client much more. I don't know how cleaned u want the source to be to call cleaned :p But I say its pretty well cleaned, and an awesome source to use.[/b]
[b]What's still in it:[/b] firemaking base runecrafting agility very descent prayer descent combat range & mage tzhaar fight pits pretty descent Edited and redid a lot of stuff
And looks like thats it. -> Much space to do your own work :D
